the app is probably crashing on your macbook air because it's a MACBOOK AIR. The highest possible processor in that thing is 2.13GHz. Check your computer's stats against the system requirements. http://usa.autodesk.com/adsk/servlet/pc/index?siteID=123112&id=15435044

NOBODY should be running a program like autocad on a computer like a macbook air. It's like asking a baby to carry an elephant on its back.
